org.bicycleGeometryWorkshop.ui.tree

Interface NavigatorListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BicycleGeometryWorkshopUI

    public interface NavigatorListener
    Listener object for the NavigatorTree. The navigator calls these in response to menu actions to notify the UI of requested actions to apply to the project.
